@Node Main "IconPlayer"

					@{b}IconPlayer@{ub}


	IconPlayer is an appicon which play ST MOD simply with Drag&Drop.


				@{" Installation - Usage " link Usage}
				@{"      The Author      " link Auteur}

@Endnode

@Node Usage

					@{b}Installation@{ub}

	IconPlayer needs OS 2.0 or greater and the ReqTools.library by Nico Franįois.


					      @{b}Usage@{ub}

	Drop the icon of the module you want to play on the IconPlayer appicon ! A short menu should appear if you click on the appicon. You can so pause the module, free the module and quit IconPlayer.


@Endnode

